  "3276440": {
    "name": "JumpKin",
    "steam_appid": 3276440,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/8643f0fbbbb4e8ba663d71ebbc17416b.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/8643f0fbbbb4e8ba663d71ebbc17416b.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/8643f0fbbbb4e8ba663d71ebbc17416b.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JumpKin 冒险开始！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入这个可爱又充满竞争的世界吧！准备好用南瓜角色挑战你的朋友了吗？在这款色彩丰富、充满活力的平台游戏中，你将同时体验乐趣和策略！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从 10 多种独特设计的角色中选择你的最爱。你会选择哪个南瓜呢？选择地图和游戏模式，决定是否开启技能，然后开始游戏吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏模式：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>南瓜狩猎：</strong> 在这个模式中，目标是捕猎对手并获得积分！当一个南瓜跳到另一个南瓜的头上时，被压的玩家会爆炸，猎杀者获得 1 分，被猎杀者失去 1 分。运用你的策略和速度，击败你的对手吧！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>皇冠争夺战：</strong> 游戏开始时，地图上会出现一顶皇冠！持有皇冠的时间越长，获得的积分就越多。快跑吧，擅长躲避和追逐的人才能赢！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>爆炸南瓜：</strong> 在这个刺激的模式中，游戏开始时，随机一名玩家会获得炸弹。你必须在炸弹爆炸前将它传递给其他玩家！如果时间到了还没甩掉炸弹，你就会爆炸！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强力技能等你来体验！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集地图上的强化道具，获得优势！但这些技能是随机且限时的，所以在正确的时间使用它们是策略的一部分。例如：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/9f6bab0731d14d8964f18677d85937d2.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/9f6bab0731d14d8964f18677d85937d2.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/9f6bab0731d14d8964f18677d85937d2.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>隐身：</strong> 让自己隐形，在不被发现的情况下得分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/ba657833cfef508b412295c3297bcb6e.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/ba657833cfef508b412295c3297bcb6e.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/ba657833cfef508b412295c3297bcb6e.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>二段跳：</strong> 轻松跨越障碍，比对手更快到达目标！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/fce958dba8673193cc22b7286144855c.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/fce958dba8673193cc22b7286144855c.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/fce958dba8673193cc22b7286144855c.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>极速奔跑：</strong> 没人能阻止你，像闪电一样在地图上飞驰！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/496827a25f588efccb7ff7a90404b9f3.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/496827a25f588efccb7ff7a90404b9f3.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/496827a25f588efccb7ff7a90404b9f3.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>护盾：</strong> 提高你的防御，即使敌人跳到你身上，你也不会失分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要注意！这些技能的持续时间有限，所以请精心策划，选择最佳时机使用它们，超越对手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最终，得分最高的玩家将获胜！但最重要的不仅仅是胜利，而是在这场充满刺激和乐趣的冒险中，谁能留下最美好的回忆！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和朋友一起比赛、挑战、享受最快乐的时光，<strong>JumpKin 的冒险</strong> 正等着你！</p>",
